sequenceDiagram
  autonumber
  actor Customer
  actor Driver
  participant Gateway as API Gateway
  participant Booking as Booking Service
  participant Ride as Ride Service
  participant Payment as Payment Service
  participant Wallet as Wallet Service
  participant MQ as RabbitMQ
  Customer->>Gateway: Confirm booking with CASH
  Gateway->>Booking: Create booking(paymentMethod=CASH)
  Booking->>Payment: Register deferred cash payment
  Payment-->>Booking: Deferred payment accepted
  Booking->>MQ: booking.confirmed
  MQ->>Ride: Create ride and dispatch driver
  Driver->>Gateway: Complete ride after collecting cash
  Gateway->>Ride: Mark ride COMPLETED
  Ride->>MQ: ride.completed(fare, driverId, CASH)
  MQ->>Payment: Finalize cash payment
  Payment->>Payment: Calculate commission and cash collected
  Payment->>Wallet: Create earning and platform debt
  alt Wallet balance covers debt
    Wallet->>Wallet: Settle oldest debt by FIFO
  else Wallet balance insufficient
    Wallet->>Wallet: Keep DebtRecord OPEN
  end
  Wallet->>MQ: driver.earning.settled / debt.updated
  Payment->>MQ: payment.finalized
  Gateway-->>Customer: Show completed cash payment
  Gateway-->>Driver: Show earning and debt status
